AGI - "I wish to address the women and men of the State Police > the most cordial greeting, on the occasion of the celebration of the 172th anniversary of foundation >. Civil passion and ethical rigour, closeness to citizens and fidelity to constitutional values, high professionalism and increasing technical specialization, constitute the distinctive traits of a Corps at the service of the community, elements that make it a valuable reference point in the life of every day". This is said by the President of the Republic, Sergio Mattarella>, in a message sent to the Chief of Police, Director-General of Public Security, Prefect Vittorio Pisani.<br> "The State Police, in accompanying the democratic life of the Country, contributes to laying the indispensable premises for the full exercise of constitutional freedoms >, in a context - continues - in which legality, social cohesion, protection of the rights and dignity of the people against every subside".
&nbsp;
"They are challenges that the State Police face every day in the fight against all forms of organized crime and terrorism, in actions to prevent and counteract the phenomena of the most impactful crime in the different areas of the country, starting from the hateful episodes of violence and aggression, especially against women. In each field, the action of the Body - Mattarella still emphasizes - aims to give effective response to safety requests to guarantee the consortium society, also on new lands, such as the digital environment, with the consequent risks of cyber-crime and cyberbullying". &nbsp;
&nbsp;
"It is &nbsp; the delicate commitment - the Head of State still observes - placed in guaranteeing the exercise of the right of reunion and manifestation of thought, together with the safety of people and the protection of goods, in a correct management of the public order, for which the Republic has given, in 2023, the Medal of gold to the Civil Valor to the women and men of the Furniture Departments, for the profused dedication in the assignment. It is the goal, in the implementation of security policies in the territories, as well as in international cooperation, of the management of the migration phenomenon that manifests itself outside the legal channels, in which precious are the experiences matured with integrated and participative approaches, which see in the field, together, institutional actors and members of civil society".
&nbsp;
"The promotion of the values of respect for the rules and fair competition, in particular among young people, implemented by the Body also through sports practice, is witnessed by the Gold Medal to the Civil Valor awarded to the Flag of the State Police, in relation to the agonistic results and initiatives of proximity and inclusion of the Golden Flames, of which this year the seventy years of constitution. In today's event - Mattarella concludes - I am grateful to express the sentiments of gratitude of the entire national community > to members of the Body for the constant and generous service provided daily. A moving thought goes to those who have lost their lives or have been injured in fulfilling the mission entrusted to them by the Republic. With such sentiments, all members of the State Police and their family members come the most intense wishes of good Feast".&nbsp;

